@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="content-page fade-in">
    <div class="glass-card">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-shield-halved" style="color: var(--accent-blue);"></i> Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="content-subtitle">Last updated: June 2026 — HITEC University Student Portal (HiSUP)</p>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-database"></i> Data Collection</h2>
            <p>HiSUP collects and stores the following student information to provide academic services:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Student identification (Name, Student ID, CNIC)</li>
                <li>Contact information (Email address)</li>
                <li>Academic records (Enrollments, courses, semester data)</li>
                <li>Financial records (Fee payments and running totals)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement enterprise-grade security measures including SQL Server Row-Level Security (RLS) 
               to ensure students can only access their own records. All database connections use session 
               context authentication for complete data isolation between users.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Data Usage</h2>
            <p>Your data is used exclusively for:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Managing course enrollments and academic records</li>
                <li>Displaying your personalized student dashboard</li>
                <li>Processing enrollment transactions through stored procedures</li>
                <li>University administrative and reporting purposes</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Your Rights</h2>
            <p>As a student you have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your personal data stored in the system</li>
                <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
                <li>Know how your data is being processed</li>
                <li>Contact the university for data-related inquiries</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact</h2>
            <p>For questions regarding your data and privacy, please contact the HITEC University 
               IT Department or visit the university administration office.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
